Clear Skies - From Astrophysics to Air Pollution
------------------------------------------------

Installation and Usage
----------------------

To work on the "pysmog" module, it's recommended to use a virtual environment
to isolate dependencies. Follow these steps to set up the environment:

> git clone https://github.com/nx1/clear_skies.git
> cd clear_skies
> python3 -m venv pysmog 
> source pysmog/bin/activate
> pip install .
> deactivate

