UK Air Information Data Archive
-------------------------------
https://uk-air.defra.gov.uk/data/
https://uk-air.defra.gov.uk/data/data_selector_service

Best way to download data is to find a site like the following:
https://www.airqualityengland.co.uk/site/data?site_id=TH2
Go to the "Download Data" tab
use Ctrl to select all metrics
https://www.airqualityengland.co.uk/assets/downloads/2022-01-01-230802122803.csv


